    "StockRole": "Fast Assault",
    "YangsThoughts": "A reworked classic mech from the past, brought back out of storage and upgraded. This thing has a decent number of missile hardpoints, but not as many as you might think for a missile boat, you're gonna need to go for bigger launchers even if they're a bit wasteful on the tonnage. It's very ammo focused as well, so it's great in vacuum where you can't cool properly. This thing also mounts these weird gauss shotgun things, which are at least good at hitting through armor."
